        <updateDate>2021-02-23T15:59:05Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Ally's Act<br> </b><br> This bill requires private health insurance plans to cover certain hearing devices and systems (e.g., bone-anchored auditory implants) and related items and services. The bill also imposes limits on cost sharing.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
